        "text": "1 Kings 18:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " we have parenthetical remarks introduced, to explain the circumstances which led to Elijah's meeting with Ahab. The verbs ויּקרא, ויהי, ויּאמר ,ויהי , and ויחלּקוּ (",
